{
  "stem": "6944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were plenty in the-- not-- not the Holocaust only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were victims because he-- he went to drink eventually because he had no future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hoffman-- and then I spoke German to him because he-- I could hear the accent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want-- I want-- the first thing I want you to do is take me to the post office.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, certainly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a car waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he drives, and didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How big is Beira?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING PORTUGUESE] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went in there, sent a telegram to my parents. 'Arrived safe and sound, all well.' I wanted my parents to be quiet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- I was a month on the boat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for that, my mom-- later I heard that my mother had taken so ill that she couldn't even get out of-- of bed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, she was frail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Secondly, she-- her wonderful precious child, her-- the apple of her eye had gone, knowing she would never see me again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that-- it was devastating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was very ill, apparently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That, I got from my surviving brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have one surviving brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That my father had to carry her out and take her to the-- to the-- there was a park nearby.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there, she sort of slowly, slowly came to herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So at least-- I didn't know that at that-- at that time, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had a telegram to say, arrived safe, all fine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now I said, you take me to Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Schwartz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And sure enough, he takes-- drives, and there's a little Schwartz and Son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, fine, you wait here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I go inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
